{"tid":969230,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"分享自己2018年歌單","createTime":"2019-01-05T01:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T12:44:31.000Z","uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef79d0ac359ee6563f7c344be6ebf620d015fbb8","tid":969230,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"排名跟播放次數<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 陳奕迅 - 我們萬歲 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢一出就down咁落黎 一個月聽咗500次 除咗謙仔哽耳嗰幾隻字 其他perfect池</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 吳雨霏 - 生命樹 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果冇上面嗰首就呢首最多 真心鍾意楊淽嗰幾首嘅作曲風格 林若寧落詞落得好中 最衰呢首冇mv<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n3. 吳雨霏 - 吳哥窟 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">陳珀作品 曲風聽落好似楊淽作嘅 都係林若寧操詞 同生命樹比較嘅話我會鍾意生命樹多啲 一黎我鍾意生命樹嘅主旨 二黎鍾意佢嘅編曲多啲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 吳雨霏 - 我本人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都係楊淽作曲 不過今次夕爺操刀落詞 當年一plug馬上大熱 個個都聽</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">不過你就咁睇都知我嘅preference係生命樹&gt;吳哥窟&gt;我本人啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 吳雨霏 - 座右銘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">作曲作詞都係我唔熟嘅 walter wong同方杰 不過產生出來嘅歌對於我呢啲毒撚就好有共鳴</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. Rubberband - 未來見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌 呢首歌唔洗講啦 好聽到傻</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7. 小肥 - 當你走了以後II-觸景傷城<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小肥呢首好正 對比起當你走了以後I嘅輕鬆曲風 呢首悲嘅感覺出晒黎 聽到佢返去以前同情人一齊嘅地方 feel到佢無力挽回呢段感情嘅哀痛</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: red;\">其實除咗呢首仲有首冒雨都好正 不過冇上我榜 唔多講 自己聽吧</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8. 陳奕迅 - 阿貓阿狗 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小弟最愛The Key嘅呢首歌 好似講緊自己咁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n9. 李克勤 - 失魂記<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">過咗咁多年 CD勤嘅唱功功力雖然失色咗少少 不過依然好聽 謙仔填詞 填得唔錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10. 張敬軒 - 不同班同學<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">軒仔近排出嘅歌比較鍾意呢首</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家都分享吓自己歌單<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1971cbb160e796c714c095e7f5145773eca8ac8a","tid":969230,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}